<p>The problem occurs in the receive function when the loop continues to call $this-&gt;_client-&gt;receive() whereas no more messages are in the queue.</p>

<p>I have seen that you're calling the "$this-&gt;_client-&gt;canRead()" method only before the beginning of the loop.</p>

<p>I have personnally added  the following test in the beginning of the loop  :
 if(!$this-&gt;_client-&gt;canRead()) {
   break;
 }
